<item>
            <title>[PIG-3016] Modernize more tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3016</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This takes the same idea as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3006&quot; title=&quot;Modernize a chunk of the tests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3006&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3006&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and applies it to the remaining tests. Note that the one thing I did not do was get rid of MiniCluster. That can be for another JIRA. All of this refactoring is effort enough for the time being &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
