                            <comment id="13486582" author="jcoveney" created="Tue, 30 Oct 2012 01:14:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a patch! It has whitespace changes. Will attach RB shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13486584" author="jcoveney" created="Tue, 30 Oct 2012 01:17:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;RB link. Keep in mind that this has all of the changes from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3006&quot; title=&quot;Modernize a chunk of the tests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3006&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3006&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (maybe I should have based the diff off that), so any file changed there isn&apos;t what this patch changed. Hopefully this will be cleaner once that patch is committed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.apache.org/r/7771/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://reviews.apache.org/r/7771/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13492897" author="cheolsoo" created="Thu, 8 Nov 2012 02:06:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Since &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3006&quot; title=&quot;Modernize a chunk of the tests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3006&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3006&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is committed now, I re-based the patch to trunk. I am uploading two patches: w/ and w/o white space changes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition to re-basing it, I made two changes as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Reverted the following change since it is not correct:
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;TestDataModel.java&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
-        assertFalse(f1.equals(f2));
+        assertEquals(f1, f2);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In several places, changed the following
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!iter.hasNext())
    fail(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;No Output received&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
assertTrue(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;No Output received&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, iter.hasNext());
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Other than this, I made no further changes to Jonathan&apos;s original patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am giving +1 to Jonathan&apos;s patch. After running a full unit test suite with both hadoop 20 and 23 tonight, I am going to commit it to trunk.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please let me know if you have any concerns.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13492958" author="jcoveney" created="Thu, 8 Nov 2012 04:58:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sounds great, Chealsoo. thanks for following through on this!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13493305" author="cheolsoo" created="Thu, 8 Nov 2012 17:08:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed to trunk. Thanks a lot Jonathan for your contribution!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
